The app.py should be put inside the root folder of OSSIM.

This python file can then be executed from with in the OSSIM when an alert is generated as following:

In OSSIM:
Go to Configuration -> Threat Intelligence -> Actions < / br>

Now before adding the path to execute the file, install python3 on OSSIM using: </ br>

apt-get install python3 </ br>

After installing python3, you would need to install theHive4py python library: </ br>

pip3 install theHive4py </ br>


